\b Manual Assessment Checklist\b0\par
\par
This Word-compatible worksheet is intended for team-based manual assessment of the six NIST SP 800-53 Rev. 5 controls represented in this repository's sample NIST control set.\par
\par
\b Assessed Controls\b0\par
- AC-2 Account Management\par
- AU-2 Event Logging\par
- IR-1 Policy and Procedures\par
- IA-5 Authenticator Management\par
- SC-7 Boundary Protection\par
- SI-4 System Monitoring\par
\par
\b Team Instructions\b0\par
1. Review each requirement.\par
2. Mark status as Pass, Partial, Fail, or Not Applicable.\par
3. Record evidence references and notes.\par
4. Capture confirmed gaps in the remediation section.\par
\par
\b Assessment Scale\b0\par
Pass = fully implemented and evidenced.\par
Partial = partly implemented or incompletely evidenced.\par
Fail = not implemented or not evidenced.\par
Not Applicable = does not apply and rationale is documented.\par
\par
