\b Remediation Summary\b0\par
AC-2: Implement authentication, unique identities, RBAC, account lifecycle workflows.\par
AU-2: Implement structured audit logging with defined event catalog and retention.\par
IR-1: Create and approve service-level incident response policy and procedures.\par
IA-5: Introduce enterprise authentication, MFA, secret rotation, and revocation procedures.\par
SC-7: Replace wildcard CORS with allowlists and document managed interfaces and boundary controls.\par
SI-4: Integrate monitoring, telemetry, alerting, and escalation workflows.\par
